Class Storyline

java.lang.Object

component.components.storyline.Storyline
All Implemented Interfaces:
Savable, SavableAsJSONObject<BasicStoryComponent>
public class Storyline
extends BasicStoryComponent
An instance of BasicStoryComponent. A storyline is a timeline containing event cards.

    • initialize

      public void initialize()
      FXML initialize method, called after Storyline.fxml finishes loading. Does the following:
      1. Sets display of all fields.
      2. Setups context menu to display when right clicked, and hide when clicked elsewhere.
      3. Setups event card to be able to be added to this storyline by drag-drop.
      4. Setups title to be editable when clicked.
      5. Setups column constraints of the eventCardContainer.
      6. Setups length of line.
